Examples of EngPatcher original work (non-exhaustive):

  - `src/` EngPatcher Python modules (except where a file is a thin wrap of
    upstream logic and notes otherwise)
  - `tools/deploy_*.py`, `tools/deploy_common.py`, `tools/rebuild_bake_img.py`,
    `tools/mdcutil.py`, and other EngPatcher-authored helpers under `tools/`
  - `Drop CIA or 3DS Here to Patch.bat`, project docs authored here
  - Finished translation / patch assets authored for this project under
    `assets/`, `rebuild_dbin2/`, and similar project paths (not third-party trees)


